1
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,030
[The Princess Royal]

2
00:01:26,030 --> 00:01:27,890
[Adapted from Mo Shubai's novel,
The Princess Royal]

3
00:01:27,890 --> 00:01:28,950
[on Jinjiang Original Network]

4
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:30,020
[This is a work of fiction.]

5
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
[Episode 1]

6
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,740
- We wish to see Your Majesty.
- We wish to see Your Majesty.

7
00:01:45,420 --> 00:01:47,300
I am the Empress

8
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,580
and the biological mother
of the Crown Prince.

9
00:01:48,780 --> 00:01:50,300
Why does His Majesty refuse to see me?

10
00:01:52,100 --> 00:01:53,220
Your Majesty, please forgive me.

11
00:01:53,420 --> 00:01:55,340
Prime Minister Pei has given an order
that no one is allowed

12
00:01:55,380 --> 00:01:58,020
to step into the Hanqiu Palace
before he arrives.

13
00:01:58,100 --> 00:01:58,780
Unit Zhun,

14
00:01:59,100 --> 00:02:00,660
no matter what changes occur in Huajing,

15
00:02:01,060 --> 00:02:02,260
no one can leave their post
without authorization.

16
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:03,620
Unit Kun,

17
00:02:03,820 --> 00:02:04,460
from this moment on,

18
00:02:04,460 --> 00:02:06,100
no one may enter
or leave the Imperial Palace.

19
00:02:06,580 --> 00:02:08,380
Those who disobey will be executed.

20
00:02:09,620 --> 00:02:10,260
Unit Meng,

21
00:02:10,980 --> 00:02:12,380
come with me to the Hanqiu Palace.

22
00:02:15,060 --> 00:02:16,020
Prime Minister Pei has arrived.

23
00:02:25,340 --> 00:02:25,740
[Pei Wenxuan]

24
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:27,380
[The Senior Grand Secretary
of the Great Xia Dynasty]

25
00:02:57,460 --> 00:02:58,100
Prime Minister Pei.

26
00:03:02,260 --> 00:03:04,100
Your Majesty,
you've come to the Hanqiu Palace

27
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:06,700
in the middle of the night
with these ministers.

28
00:03:07,660 --> 00:03:08,900
Do you intend to force an abdication?

29
00:03:08,940 --> 00:03:10,340
[Shangguan Ya,
Empress of the Great Xia Dynasty]

30
00:03:10,340 --> 00:03:11,020
Prime Minister Pei,

31
00:03:11,340 --> 00:03:12,700
His Majesty has been waiting for you.

32
00:03:13,460 --> 00:03:14,060
Please.

33
00:03:15,580 --> 00:03:16,540
You may all leave now.

34
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:22,460
[Hanqiu Palace]

35
00:03:22,700 --> 00:03:24,340
Send a message
to Second Young Master immediately.

36
00:03:24,660 --> 00:03:26,260
Tell him to stay on standby.

37
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:27,380
Yes, Your Majesty.

38
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:56,980
You are awake, Your Highness.

39
00:03:58,100 --> 00:04:01,020
This is freshly brewed pear soup.

40
00:04:01,300 --> 00:04:03,540
[Second Young Master Su]
Take a sip to wet your whistle.

41
00:04:03,540 --> 00:04:03,860
[Vice Minister of Justice]

42
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:06,500
[Li Rong, Princess Royal]

43
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:07,140
Okay.

44
00:04:19,180 --> 00:04:20,140
You are here.

45
00:04:22,100 --> 00:04:24,620
[Li Chuan, Emperor]

46
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:25,980
Your Majesty,

47
00:04:27,300 --> 00:04:28,500
do you want to leave a message?

48
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,540
Depose Crown Prince Li Xin

49
00:04:31,780 --> 00:04:34,460
and let the Eldest Prince Li Ping
inherit the throne.

50
00:04:34,940 --> 00:04:36,380
I have already prepared everything

51
00:04:37,620 --> 00:04:38,860
on my way here.

52
00:04:41,940 --> 00:04:45,220
[Depose him
from the position of Crown Prince]

53
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:49,780
Since the founding of the Xia Dynasty,

54
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:52,860
the power has always been in the hands
of the Noble Houses.

55
00:04:54,540 --> 00:04:56,460
Although my Li Family is royalty,

56
00:04:57,380 --> 00:04:59,580
we are merely puppets
of the Noble Houses.

57
00:05:00,060 --> 00:05:01,940
It is only when facing death

58
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:04,620
that I realize my eldest sister,

59
00:05:07,020 --> 00:05:08,940
Princess Royal Li Rong,

60
00:05:10,180 --> 00:05:12,740
is the true power
behind the Noble Houses.

61
00:05:15,060 --> 00:05:16,260
After my demise,

62
00:05:17,820 --> 00:05:19,820
if the Princess Royal plots a rebellion,

63
00:05:20,940 --> 00:05:23,820
how should you, her nominal husband

64
00:05:24,380 --> 00:05:27,620
and the representative
of the commoners, respond,

65
00:05:31,580 --> 00:05:33,060
Prime Minister Pei?

66
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:35,140
The nation belongs to the people.

67
00:05:35,860 --> 00:05:37,420
As long as I am here,

68
00:05:38,180 --> 00:05:39,020
the commoners

69
00:05:40,940 --> 00:05:42,300
will not fall into decline.

70
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:46,860
What is the situation
with the Crown Prince's succession?

71
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:49,700
Prime Minister Pei refuses to relent

72
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:52,620
and insists on following
His Majesty's wishes

73
00:05:53,020 --> 00:05:54,700
to appoint the Eldest Prince Li Ping
as the Crown Prince.

74
00:05:55,140 --> 00:05:56,620
Pei Wenxuan intends to make Li Ping
the Crown Prince.

75
00:05:58,380 --> 00:06:01,060
We, the Noble Houses,
will be their biggest obstacle.

76
00:06:02,380 --> 00:06:04,260
Therefore, before he makes a move...

77
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:08,420
Before Pei Wenxuan makes a move...

78
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:09,380
Your Highness, rest assured.

79
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:13,500
Everything has been arranged properly.

80
00:06:15,820 --> 00:06:16,620
That's good to know.

81
00:06:19,420 --> 00:06:20,620
If I died,

82
00:06:22,020 --> 00:06:23,700
Pei Wenxuan would have unmatched power.

83
00:06:24,380 --> 00:06:25,460
If you died,

84
00:06:27,380 --> 00:06:28,500
he wouldn't survive either.

85
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:30,860
I'd kill him

86
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:33,740
to let him be buried with you.

87
00:06:47,860 --> 00:06:48,940
I never realized

88
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:52,220
that our Young Master Su,
so elegant and composed,

89
00:06:53,340 --> 00:06:54,980
could also get angry.

90
00:06:55,460 --> 00:06:57,340
There are lots of things
that can make me angry,

91
00:06:58,500 --> 00:06:59,300
for example...

92
00:06:59,900 --> 00:07:02,420
Your Highness, Prime Minister Pei
requests an audience.

93
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:07,700
If Your Highness prefers not to see him,

94
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:10,100
I'll go and send him away.

95
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:12,140
After all, we are husband and wife,

96
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:14,980
and we haven't divorced yet.

97
00:07:17,540 --> 00:07:18,700
I shall go and see him.

98
00:07:19,860 --> 00:07:20,660
Probably,

99
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:23,100
this will be our final meeting.

100
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:30,500
You may leave now.

101
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:38,100
Ask him to leave.

102
00:07:56,100 --> 00:07:56,740
Rongqing.

103
00:08:00,220 --> 00:08:02,020
Could you get me a cup of tea, please?

104
00:08:08,780 --> 00:08:10,140
Then please take care of yourself.

105
00:08:10,140 --> 00:08:11,980
I promise not to get angry.

106
00:08:22,340 --> 00:08:23,140
What do you come to see me for?

107
00:08:25,380 --> 00:08:26,500
I've come today

108
00:08:26,860 --> 00:08:28,780
to discuss the matter
of appointing the Crown Prince with you.

109
00:08:30,580 --> 00:08:32,900
Xin is the biological son
of the Empress Shangguan Ya.

110
00:08:33,340 --> 00:08:35,340
He is modest, respectful,
and utterly worthy of the position.

111
00:08:36,180 --> 00:08:37,620
What's there to discuss?

112
00:08:41,140 --> 00:08:43,540
The Third Prince Li Xin
is arrogant and unruly,

113
00:08:43,980 --> 00:08:45,580
which makes him unsuitable
for the position of Crown Prince.

114
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:48,740
His mother, Shangguan,
holds too much power.

115
00:08:49,420 --> 00:08:51,060
If something were to happen
to you and me in the future...

116
00:08:51,220 --> 00:08:52,900
Why is he also wearing the sachet?

117
00:08:54,260 --> 00:08:55,820
And the fragrance is so strong.

118
00:08:59,300 --> 00:09:01,220
You're saying high-sounding words.

119
00:09:01,900 --> 00:09:02,700
But you know exactly

120
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:04,060
what your true purpose is.

121
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:08,420
Do you insist on letting Li Xin
ascend the throne?

122
00:09:08,420 --> 00:09:10,100
Xin is the biological son
of the Empress.

123
00:09:11,020 --> 00:09:12,220
Are we really
going to let a concubine's son

124
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:13,700
ascend the throne instead?

125
00:09:13,700 --> 00:09:15,180
Are you still holding a grudge
against Zhen?

126
00:09:18,380 --> 00:09:20,380
Can you please address her
as Imperial Concubine Qin?

127
00:09:22,420 --> 00:09:24,420
How can you call her Zhen?

128
00:09:25,860 --> 00:09:26,900
Don't forget

129
00:09:27,220 --> 00:09:28,700
that the Qin Zhenzhen you adore

130
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:29,740
is my younger brother,

131
00:09:29,740 --> 00:09:32,220
the current Emperor Li Chuan's
deceased concubine.

132
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:35,820
Her child Li Ping cannot
become the Crown Prince.

133
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:42,260
You can still talk this much with me.

134
00:09:43,660 --> 00:09:45,020
It seems

135
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:47,580
you are not as frail
as has been rumored.

136
00:09:52,500 --> 00:09:54,100
If you disagree, so be it.

137
00:09:55,140 --> 00:09:56,780
We'll each handle things
our own way later on.

138
00:09:57,620 --> 00:09:59,460
But don't blame me
for not reminding you.

139
00:10:00,260 --> 00:10:01,460
I'd like to know

140
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:04,540
what your way will be.

141
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:06,220
Whatever way you think it is.

142
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:07,980
What? Are you going to kill me?

143
00:10:08,340 --> 00:10:09,540
Do you think I don't dare to do so?

144
00:10:16,660 --> 00:10:17,620
Pei Wenxuan,

145
00:10:19,540 --> 00:10:21,340
do you really want to sacrifice
the well-being of the whole world

146
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:23,660
for your own selfish desires?

147
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:25,500
What capabilities do I possess

148
00:10:25,900 --> 00:10:27,220
to influence the whole world?

149
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:28,860
However, the person
favored by Your Highness

150
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:31,260
may not necessarily
be of good character.

151
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:33,140
What's the point of him,
a castrated man,

152
00:10:33,140 --> 00:10:34,620
currying favor with you here?

153
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:35,460
What did you say?

154
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:36,620
Pei Wenxuan.

155
00:10:36,780 --> 00:10:37,460
Pei Wenxuan,

156
00:10:37,460 --> 00:10:39,380
I won't allow you
to slander Rongqing in the slightest!

157
00:11:15,420 --> 00:11:16,780
We agreed not to get angry,

158
00:11:17,300 --> 00:11:18,900
so why are you
getting so worked up again?

159
00:11:19,660 --> 00:11:20,660
Go fetch the medicine for Her Highness.

160
00:11:20,900 --> 00:11:21,660
- Yes.
- Yes.

161
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:23,940
He's definitely up to no good
coming to see you here.

162
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:26,940
You're still unwell,
so why bother seeing him?

163
00:11:27,260 --> 00:11:28,060
I'm fine.

164
00:11:53,420 --> 00:11:54,060
What's wrong?

165
00:11:58,420 --> 00:12:00,300
Imperial Physician!
Get the Imperial Physician now!

166
00:12:04,780 --> 00:12:06,580
It's the Poison of the Fragrant Beauty.

167
00:12:20,580 --> 00:12:21,420
Pei Wenxuan.

168
00:12:23,180 --> 00:12:24,020
It's Pei Wenxuan.

169
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:26,900
The sachet he was wearing...

170
00:12:34,060 --> 00:12:36,460
Rong, stop talking.

171
00:12:37,380 --> 00:12:38,500
Conserve your strength.

172
00:12:40,700 --> 00:12:41,460
I'm sorry.

173
00:12:42,580 --> 00:12:43,980
I failed to protect you.

174
00:12:44,860 --> 00:12:47,140
He finally made his move against me.

175
00:12:51,860 --> 00:12:52,580
Heed my order.

176
00:12:54,580 --> 00:12:55,780
If I die,

177
00:12:57,500 --> 00:12:58,420
Pei Wenxuan...

178
00:13:00,980 --> 00:13:02,020
cannot live.

179
00:13:15,620 --> 00:13:18,260
Young Master,
I feel something's not right.

180
00:13:18,260 --> 00:13:20,220
[Tong Ye, Pei Wenxuan's valet]
Could it be that the Princess's Mansion

181
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:21,060
has sent someone to follow us?

182
00:13:22,220 --> 00:13:23,260
Ignore them.

183
00:13:23,380 --> 00:13:24,980
How can we ignore them?

184
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:26,540
She's just trying to scare me.

185
00:13:26,540 --> 00:13:27,980
She won't actually kill me.

186
00:15:01,620 --> 00:15:03,220
Whose order are you following?

187
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:06,740
By order of the Princess Royal,

188
00:15:07,100 --> 00:15:08,260
you shall be killed without mercy.

189
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:13,420
I never thought

190
00:15:15,260 --> 00:15:18,060
you would eventually attack me.

191
00:15:24,140 --> 00:15:26,780
You are the only weal and woe...

192
00:15:29,180 --> 00:15:30,580
that I cannot avoid in my lifetime.

193
00:15:44,100 --> 00:15:45,820
What's the situation
with that person now?

194
00:15:46,260 --> 00:15:47,260
It's all sorted.

195
00:15:52,300 --> 00:15:53,580
For twenty years,

196
00:15:55,900 --> 00:15:58,260
I've been entangled with him.

197
00:16:01,140 --> 00:16:02,420
I've never expected it

198
00:16:05,140 --> 00:16:07,380
to end like this.

199
00:16:07,740 --> 00:16:10,860
It's all over between you and him.

200
00:16:11,820 --> 00:16:13,260
None of us

201
00:16:17,860 --> 00:16:19,340
are worthy of Your Highness.

202
00:16:29,660 --> 00:16:31,420
My greatest regret...

203
00:16:33,860 --> 00:16:36,220
in this lifetime...

204
00:16:39,700 --> 00:16:40,780
is...

205
00:16:42,340 --> 00:16:44,420
missing you.

206
00:16:47,460 --> 00:16:48,940
If only

207
00:16:49,900 --> 00:16:51,620
I could dream a great dream

208
00:16:53,220 --> 00:16:54,260
and I could start...

209
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:01,540
everything anew.

210
00:17:11,620 --> 00:17:15,540
The Princess Royal has passed away.

211
00:17:29,540 --> 00:17:30,620
Where am I?

212
00:18:29,380 --> 00:18:30,300
It's been a while,

213
00:18:31,500 --> 00:18:33,020
warm sunshine.

214
00:18:44,300 --> 00:18:46,460
Your Highness, you're awake.

215
00:18:47,700 --> 00:18:48,500
Jinglan?

216
00:18:49,540 --> 00:18:50,820
What's going on?

217
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:52,820
How come she's not dead?

218
00:18:52,980 --> 00:18:56,380
Jinglan, aren't you...

219
00:19:00,260 --> 00:19:01,140
Watch out, Your Highness.

220
00:19:06,900 --> 00:19:07,860
Could it be

221
00:19:09,020 --> 00:19:10,540
that we're now meeting
in the underworld?

222
00:19:14,140 --> 00:19:16,300
Your Highness, it hurts.

223
00:19:17,860 --> 00:19:19,060
You really are alive.

224
00:19:19,820 --> 00:19:21,100
You are not dead.

225
00:19:22,420 --> 00:19:25,740
Your Highness,
why are you wishing me dead

226
00:19:25,940 --> 00:19:28,140
when there's nothing happened?

227
00:19:29,380 --> 00:19:31,020
I don't know
whether the past was a dream

228
00:19:32,580 --> 00:19:33,940
or the present is a dream,

229
00:19:35,460 --> 00:19:38,660
but luckily, you're still alive.

230
00:19:39,940 --> 00:19:40,940
That's great.

231
00:19:41,060 --> 00:19:43,420
Your Highness, are you all right?

232
00:19:43,980 --> 00:19:45,620
It's already the hour of Si.
[*9 AM to 11 AM]

233
00:19:45,980 --> 00:19:47,180
His Majesty held court
and has just finished it.

234
00:19:47,340 --> 00:19:48,420
He has sent word for you

235
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:50,820
to join him for lunch.

236
00:19:51,300 --> 00:19:52,980
I was just about to come and wake you.

237
00:19:53,260 --> 00:19:54,620
But you are already awake.

238
00:19:56,300 --> 00:19:57,700
You said His Majesty
had just finished court?

239
00:19:58,780 --> 00:19:59,700
That's great.

240
00:20:00,660 --> 00:20:03,380
The message from the palace
said his days were numbered.

241
00:20:05,100 --> 00:20:05,820
By the way,

242
00:20:06,540 --> 00:20:08,020
how about that rascal Pei Wenxuan?

243
00:20:08,740 --> 00:20:09,420
Has he died yet?

244
00:20:09,900 --> 00:20:12,580
Who is this Pei Wenxuan?

245
00:20:13,820 --> 00:20:15,540
Do you have a grudge against him?

246
00:20:40,500 --> 00:20:41,980
The Poison of the Fragrant Beauty

247
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:44,300
not only failed to kill me

248
00:20:44,700 --> 00:20:46,820
but also had the miraculous effect
of rejuvenating me.

249
00:20:56,460 --> 00:20:57,260
Your Highness.

250
00:20:57,700 --> 00:20:59,020
This isn't the Princess Royal's Mansion,

251
00:20:59,860 --> 00:21:01,820
but the Changle Palace
where I lived before getting married.

252
00:21:06,780 --> 00:21:08,620
My body feels so light.

253
00:21:24,300 --> 00:21:26,780
Your Highness, where are you going?

254
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:29,580
Please slow down.

255
00:21:53,660 --> 00:21:56,540
Your Highness.

256
00:21:58,220 --> 00:21:59,860
What's happening to you, Your Highness?

257
00:22:03,260 --> 00:22:04,260
Tell me

258
00:22:05,140 --> 00:22:06,740
what year it is now.

259
00:22:07,140 --> 00:22:08,060
It's...

260
00:22:08,740 --> 00:22:10,940
It's the twenty-fourth year
of the Yongning Era now.

261
00:22:11,180 --> 00:22:12,740
The twenty-fourth year
of the Yongning Era?

262
00:22:16,860 --> 00:22:17,820
This year,

263
00:22:19,780 --> 00:22:20,900
I am eighteen years old.

264
00:22:22,940 --> 00:22:24,300
I am not yet married,

265
00:22:26,780 --> 00:22:30,620
and neither you
nor Father have passed away.

266
00:22:35,100 --> 00:22:37,020
What on earth is going on?

267
00:22:40,380 --> 00:22:42,060
Could it be that even heaven feels

268
00:22:42,180 --> 00:22:44,340
that the old me lived
too constrained a life?

269
00:22:44,940 --> 00:22:46,540
You are just like your mother,
wanting to control the royal family

270
00:22:46,740 --> 00:22:49,180
with the support
of the Shangguan Family.

271
00:22:49,180 --> 00:22:50,900
If one day I ascended the throne,

272
00:22:51,140 --> 00:22:53,700
would you also pressure me like
how the Noble Houses

273
00:22:53,820 --> 00:22:54,740
pressured Father?

274
00:22:56,340 --> 00:22:57,820
What is your relationship with her?

275
00:22:58,260 --> 00:22:59,620
Childhood friends.

276
00:23:06,100 --> 00:23:06,940
I wonder

277
00:23:07,620 --> 00:23:09,500
how Rongqing is doing now.

278
00:23:10,740 --> 00:23:12,380
I must have been blind

279
00:23:13,020 --> 00:23:14,460
to have chosen that rascal Pei Wenxuan.

280
00:23:14,700 --> 00:23:16,380
