281
00:23:17,060 --> 00:23:19,340
This time, just you wait.

282
00:23:21,940 --> 00:23:22,700
Your Highness,

283
00:23:24,740 --> 00:23:25,900
we shall get going.

284
00:23:26,300 --> 00:23:27,980
We can't keep His Majesty waiting.

285
00:23:31,420 --> 00:23:32,340
Do you know

286
00:23:33,180 --> 00:23:36,300
why Father has summoned me for a meal?

287
00:23:36,780 --> 00:23:37,580
His Majesty

288
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:40,460
wants to choose a consort for you.

289
00:23:45,460 --> 00:23:47,380
So here I am, facing
another meal of hidden dangers.

290
00:23:49,100 --> 00:23:50,100
It's such a coincidence

291
00:23:50,620 --> 00:23:51,860
that I've come back to this day.

292
00:23:52,580 --> 00:23:54,260
Since heaven has given me

293
00:23:54,260 --> 00:23:55,340
another chance,

294
00:23:55,980 --> 00:23:57,740
I won't repeat my past mistakes.

295
00:23:58,380 --> 00:24:00,660
Pei Wenxuan,
you'd better not be on the list.

296
00:24:03,220 --> 00:24:03,900
Help me get dressed.

297
00:24:44,580 --> 00:24:45,460
Your Highness.

298
00:25:18,740 --> 00:25:19,580
Pei Wenxuan,

299
00:25:22,100 --> 00:25:24,060
no matter why we end up together,

300
00:25:24,940 --> 00:25:26,140
now that we're married,

301
00:25:27,660 --> 00:25:29,820
I still want to spend
a lifetime with you.

302
00:25:32,700 --> 00:25:33,820
I am deeply honored

303
00:25:34,980 --> 00:25:36,700
and will be eternally grateful
and repay your favor.

304
00:25:37,540 --> 00:25:40,620
In that case, our primary concern

305
00:25:41,180 --> 00:25:43,340
going forward will be honesty.

306
00:25:47,340 --> 00:25:48,500
Despite our initial vows,

307
00:25:49,380 --> 00:25:51,060
he, like everyone else in this palace,

308
00:25:51,900 --> 00:25:54,420
inevitably leaned towards power
and personal gain.

309
00:25:54,460 --> 00:25:56,790
[Hanqiu Palace]

310
00:26:09,780 --> 00:26:11,420
I haven't seen Father in over ten years.

311
00:26:11,860 --> 00:26:13,540
Has he already aged so much

312
00:26:13,660 --> 00:26:15,340
[Li Ming, Emperor]
since I was eighteen?

313
00:26:17,740 --> 00:26:18,420
Father,

314
00:26:19,220 --> 00:26:20,500
if everything were to start over,

315
00:26:21,180 --> 00:26:24,620
could we just be a common father
and daughter from an ordinary family?

316
00:26:32,060 --> 00:26:33,500
Why are you standing at the doorway?

317
00:26:37,740 --> 00:26:38,460
I...

318
00:26:39,780 --> 00:26:42,300
I'm here to greet you, Father.

319
00:26:43,260 --> 00:26:43,900
You may rise.

320
00:26:45,300 --> 00:26:46,860
Come join me for the meal.

321
00:26:56,900 --> 00:26:57,620
Father,

322
00:26:58,340 --> 00:26:59,980
this is the chestnut cake
