336
00:27:50,820 --> 00:27:51,860
That's very thoughtful of you, Rong.

337
00:27:53,660 --> 00:27:56,060
Father, why are you inviting me

338
00:27:56,220 --> 00:27:57,700
to have a meal with you today?

339
00:27:58,300 --> 00:27:58,900
Fu Lai.

340
00:27:58,900 --> 00:27:59,580
Someone.

341
00:28:00,460 --> 00:28:01,540
Your Highness, please take a look.

342
00:28:02,180 --> 00:28:05,260
The first one is Lu Yu,
the son of Marquis Ningguo, Lu Tingwei.

343
00:28:05,740 --> 00:28:09,260
He was granted the title
of hereditary marquis by royal decree.

344
00:28:10,060 --> 00:28:10,700
The second one is Yang Quan,

345
00:28:11,380 --> 00:28:14,620
the second son of Grand Marshal,
Yang Ye.

346
00:28:14,860 --> 00:28:17,250
He was granted the title
of first-class major general

347
00:28:17,250 --> 00:28:17,980
by royal decree.

348
00:28:18,740 --> 00:28:19,780
The third one

349
00:28:20,260 --> 00:28:22,940
is the newly acclaimed scholar,
Cui Yulang.

350
00:28:23,780 --> 00:28:25,820
It's exactly the same as before.

351
00:28:25,820 --> 00:28:26,700
The fourth one is Pei Wenxuan,

352
00:28:26,700 --> 00:28:29,420
the son of the former Vice Minister
of Rites, Pei Lizhi,

353
00:28:29,540 --> 00:28:31,470
He was the top candidate recommended

354
00:28:31,470 --> 00:28:33,620
in the twenty-second year
of the Yongning Era.

355
00:28:40,260 --> 00:28:41,940
What is meant to come has come.

356
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:43,220
There's no escaping it in the end.

357
00:28:48,940 --> 00:28:49,900
Father.

358
00:28:51,180 --> 00:28:54,140
Recently, everyone in the court
has been talking about your marriage.

359
00:28:55,100 --> 00:28:57,060
I was thinking it was about time
for you to get married,

360
00:28:57,380 --> 00:28:58,580
so I called you over to see

361
00:28:59,660 --> 00:29:00,820
if any of these four young men

362
00:29:01,220 --> 00:29:02,660
catch your eye.

363
00:29:16,180 --> 00:29:16,900
What's the matter?

364
00:29:17,060 --> 00:29:18,460
None of them attract you?

365
00:29:20,100 --> 00:29:22,540
