366
00:29:24,180 --> 00:29:25,820
Just pick one that you find agreeable

367
00:29:26,140 --> 00:29:28,300
and I will take care of the rest.

368
00:29:28,300 --> 00:29:29,340
Everything is just as before.

369
00:29:30,180 --> 00:29:31,540
I am merely a pawn for Father

370
00:29:31,900 --> 00:29:34,020
