any of them appealing.

372
00:29:38,540 --> 00:29:40,100
It's just that they all look

373
00:29:41,260 --> 00:29:42,380
so handsome.

374
00:29:42,540 --> 00:29:43,460
I want them all.

375
00:29:43,980 --> 00:29:44,660
Don't be ridiculous.

376
00:29:46,340 --> 00:29:47,220
All of you, leave.

377
00:29:48,060 --> 00:29:49,180
I'll take my leave, Your Highness.

378
00:29:52,220 --> 00:29:53,620
If I did allow you to do that,

379
00:29:54,100 --> 00:29:56,700
then I might receive countless memorials
from the ministers

380
00:29:57,060 --> 00:29:58,460
in the future.

381
00:29:59,940 --> 00:30:03,060
Father, I was just joking.

382
00:30:03,780 --> 00:30:04,700
Isn't one's moral quality

383
00:30:04,780 --> 00:30:07,420
