384
00:30:07,420 --> 00:30:08,340
rather than his appearance?

385
00:30:08,340 --> 00:30:10,540
I can't tell much just by looks alone.

386
00:30:11,180 --> 00:30:12,060
How about this?

387
00:30:12,620 --> 00:30:14,340
You allow me to dress up

388
00:30:14,340 --> 00:30:15,740
