to go out of the palace for a bit.

394
00:30:24,460 --> 00:30:25,420
I've heard

395
00:30:25,620 --> 00:30:27,220
that the roasted duck
at the Linglong Pavilion is the best

396
00:30:27,220 --> 00:30:28,180
and the peach blossoms
at the Huguo Temple are stunning.

397
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:28,940
Alright, alright.

398
00:30:30,260 --> 00:30:32,580
Are you planning
to meet your future husband

399
00:30:32,980 --> 00:30:34,540
or just wanting to go out and have fun?

400
00:30:35,020 --> 00:30:35,820
Father.

401
00:30:37,100 --> 00:30:40,420
Father, please agree to my request.

402
00:30:40,540 --> 00:30:41,700
Father, please.

403
00:30:42,540 --> 00:30:44,340
The Spring Banquet
is right around the corner anyway.

404
00:30:46,340 --> 00:30:48,620
Then why not use the Spring Banquet
as an opportunity to meet them?

405
00:30:50,100 --> 00:30:52,220
Invite these four young men over.

406
00:30:52,580 --> 00:30:54,740
You can meet them and have a chat.

407
00:31:00,060 --> 00:31:00,780
What is it?

408
00:31:01,700 --> 00:31:03,260
Do you have any other concerns?

409
00:31:03,340 --> 00:31:04,340
I think

410
00:31:05,020 --> 00:31:06,380
if we only invite those four,

411
00:31:06,380 --> 00:31:07,740
it might be too obvious.

412
00:31:08,140 --> 00:31:10,380
Why not invite more young men
from the Noble Houses?

413
00:31:11,700 --> 00:31:12,540
We will only know if a man is good

414
00:31:12,540 --> 00:31:14,020
when there's a comparison.

415
00:31:14,380 --> 00:31:16,580
With so many young gentlemen
standing together,

416
00:31:16,580 --> 00:31:17,220
I'll be able to tell who's good

417
00:31:17,220 --> 00:31:18,620
and who's bad at a glance.

418
00:31:19,620 --> 00:31:20,580
What do you think, Father?

419
00:31:21,620 --> 00:31:22,660
That's quite an idea.

420
00:31:25,340 --> 00:31:26,500
You do have a lot of clever ideas.

421
00:31:31,460 --> 00:31:32,420
Thank you, Father.

422
00:31:44,460 --> 00:31:46,380
[Princess Royal]
Young Master.

423
00:31:50,020 --> 00:31:50,660
Young Master.

424
00:31:51,340 --> 00:31:52,380
Great news.

425
00:31:52,780 --> 00:31:54,260
Incredibly great news.

426
00:31:54,260 --> 00:31:55,060
Tong Ye?

427
00:31:58,220 --> 00:32:00,500
How come you look so young?

428
00:32:01,660 --> 00:32:04,460
I look young?

429
00:32:06,420 --> 00:32:07,620
Am I dreaming?

430
00:32:09,020 --> 00:32:10,060
Young Master, are you alright?

431
00:32:11,500 --> 00:32:13,540
Are you upset about Miss Qin
calling off the engagement?

432
00:32:14,700 --> 00:32:16,340
Don't take it to heart.

433
00:32:16,340 --> 00:32:18,180
Her calling off the engagement
is her loss.

434
00:32:18,180 --> 00:32:18,740
Hold on.

435
00:32:19,820 --> 00:32:22,020
What date is today?

436
00:32:23,020 --> 00:32:23,890
The first day of the third month

437
00:32:23,890 --> 00:32:24,980
in the twenty-fourth year
of the Yongning Era.

438
00:32:25,860 --> 00:32:28,140
Young Master, please remember today.

439
00:32:28,380 --> 00:32:31,220
It's a hugely auspicious day.

440
00:32:31,420 --> 00:32:32,380
What auspicious day?

441
00:32:32,700 --> 00:32:34,100
I'll be brief.

442
00:32:36,860 --> 00:32:38,820
Things haven't been going well
