to turn things around for you.

453
00:33:01,220 --> 00:33:03,940
And I went to offer incense
to ancestors.

454
00:33:03,940 --> 00:33:04,980
Get to the point.

455
00:33:05,340 --> 00:33:06,380
Here comes the point.

456
00:33:06,940 --> 00:33:08,060
As soon as I made a wish

457
00:33:08,060 --> 00:33:09,540
