458
00:33:09,540 --> 00:33:11,300
Master seems to have blessed us.

459
00:33:11,580 --> 00:33:12,340
Do you know?

460
00:33:12,860 --> 00:33:14,940
Princess Pingyue sent her maid

461
00:33:15,020 --> 00:33:17,260
