has been oppressing you.

474
00:33:42,380 --> 00:33:43,500
He doesn't give you the money
when you ask for it.

475
00:33:43,500 --> 00:33:44,540
And he doesn't give you the power
when you need it.

476
00:33:44,860 --> 00:33:46,460
I'm telling you, it's probably

477
00:33:46,740 --> 00:33:48,060
those scoundrels

478
00:33:48,060 --> 00:33:48,980
causing all this trouble.

479
00:33:49,300 --> 00:33:50,420
Can you be quiet for a moment?

480
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:54,940
From now on,
don't ever mention this matter anymore.

481
00:33:55,100 --> 00:33:57,260
Yes. Then you should stop being sad.

482
00:33:59,180 --> 00:34:00,220
Is this my karma?

483
00:34:00,500 --> 00:34:02,620
I've returned to my most destitute time.

